provisions.content:
(1) It-titolu ta’ dawn l-ordinamenti hu Ordinamenti g]allGrad ta’ Master of Arts in Family Ministry ta]t il-patro`inju talFakultà tal-Teolo[ija.

Titolu u tifsir.

(2) F’dawn l-ordinamenti, kemm-il darba r-rabta tal-kliem ma
te]tie[x xort’o]ra "il-Bord" tfisser il-Bord tal-Fakultà tat-Teolo[ija;
"il-Grad" tfisser il-grad ta’ Master of Arts in Family Ministry;
"il-kors" tfisser il-programm ta’ studju li jwassal g]all-grad ta’
Master of Arts in Family Ministry;
"il-Postgraduate Certificate" tfisser il-Postgraduate Certificate
in Family Ministry;
"il-Postgraduate Diploma" tfisser il-Postgraduate Diploma in
Family Ministry; u
"ir-Regolamenti Prin`ipali" tfisser ir-Regolamenti {enerali g]arRikonoxximenti Universitarji ta’ wara l-Ewwel Grad.

L.S. 327.328
